# --- Scraper local outputs ---
# The scraper writes raw per-source JSONs to scraper/data/ during a
# local dev run. They're not committed — only the dedupe step's
# unified.json (in public/data/unified.json) is. Per-source JSONs from
# CI are uploaded as GitHub Actions artifacts with 30-day retention.
scraper/data/
dedupe_output/

